Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ourarch-enemy Naraku had\ntotally concealed himself from us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fifty years ago, Onigumo the brigand\ngave rise to Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:49.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rasetsu Kansuke, who harbored a\n{\i1}deep grudge against Onigumo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}met Kikyo shortly before\nhis death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just about that time, as we journeyed\nin our search for Naraku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a chance meeting awaited us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems like such a peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sign that Naraku's been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every field is in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A boar, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- There!\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Please wait!\N- Villagers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there... the silver haired one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those ears!\NHe's not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do they mean you, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please save us, Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:50.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog God?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:54.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog God? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this? Pickled vegetables?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We realize that for someone\nof your stature,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,pickled vegetables\nmay not suffice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this is all we have in\nthe village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:20.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have no choice but\nto appeal to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!\NFan him! Fan him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:26.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Appeal to Inuyasha?\NThey must be very desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ourfields are being ravaged\nby monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:32.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monkeys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have long heard that monkeys\nfeardogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, Dog God,\nlend us yourpowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please exterminate the monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm no Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with a little monkey business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango and I will continue on\nand keep searching for Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, we can't ignore\nthe villagers' plight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn... what a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why should I deal with monkeys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:16.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.\NYou're the Dog God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup, the Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Demon Monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog Demon, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the villagers, knowing how\NI hate dogs, hired you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you'll die instead...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now this is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's better when the opponent's\na demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Little monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:58.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you the ones\nplundering the village fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As proof that we'll never\ndo evil again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,please accept our spiritual stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:12.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Since you put it that way,\NI have to accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:17.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a basic trick in\nthe mini-demon world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to catch your enemy off guard\nand make an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I don't think you should accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The dog demon can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moon, moon!\NMonkey butts are crimson red!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better cut out your silly tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless threatening us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until our spell is broken,\nyou're stuck to the rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'lljust clobber you\nwith this hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:13.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afterthem, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww... hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:31.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like they said, only the\nperpetrators can undo the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, weren't we supposed\nto look for signs of Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't have Inuyasha who can\nsniff out Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:44.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nordo we have Kagome who\ncan sense the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:51.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had to say that or Inuyasha\nwouldn't have lifted a finger to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd better shape up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd better do something!\NI'd better do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Combine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Smashing Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spinning acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Time for a snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you keep pillaging\nthe fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're not pillaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're looking for the Monkey God\nwho has been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monkey God?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:24.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The deity who was enshrined\nin this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:28.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As sprites who serve\nthe Monkey God,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:31.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ourjob was to protect the shrine\nwhile continuing our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But because of the war,\nthe shrine was burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:40.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the sacred object containing\nthe spirit of the Monkey God was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you think that the sacred object\nis in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:45.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:51.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We believe that the sacred object is\nburied in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:55.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know this because\NI had a dream message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:02.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The message said ourgod was\nin a dark, dank place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mine said it was small\nand suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:09.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In my dream, our god said\nit smelled of vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something's coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen... I won't make any\njudgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the spell you put on Inuyasha...\nyou should break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've forgotten how\nto undo the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:37.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you feign ignorance,\nyou'll get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:44.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha doesn't know how\nto take it easy with kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're not feigning ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We really did forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:57.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:01.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we find the Monkey God,\nyour spell can be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:05.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, we learned the trick\nfrom the Monkey God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must hurry back to the village\nand find the sacred object!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shoulda just waited back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you tired, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:23.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way am I gonna keep\nhanging on to this... rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How clumsy, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at you, mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a shame that you can't\nuse Tetsusaiga with that arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- How wasteful...\N- Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can leave Kagome to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, yourelderbrother, shall\ngladly use Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait... - !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way will I wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sacred object of\nthe Monkey God?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it's supposed to be\nin this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Yeah, you have it!\N- Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know of no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the hold-up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ourlives are at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Dog God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's the Monkey God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get this rock off,\nor I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was quick, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, don'tgo nearhim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:35.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:38.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you remember how to\nundo this spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourhand got stuck to the boulder\ndue to a spell those monkeys put on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really a Dog God?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:51.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I've been telling you,\NI'm not!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the farthest thing\nfrom a God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:57.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only the Monkey God can\nundo the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So if you're hiding anything,\NI'll destroy the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we split up and search?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't want anymore plundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what's it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a rock about this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's engraved with the\nsymbol of the Monkey God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's perfectly round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could that be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was a rock like that\nup in the mountain in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- It's in the mountain!\N- The mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright! The mountain\noverin the back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- This one?\N- Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remember seeing it\nalong this riverbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- The riverbed!\N- The riverbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The riverbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:55.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't look godly at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe it's that rock\nin the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next to the Jizo shrine\noverin the east...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know! The one over\nin the south valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was a rock under\nthe house...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys help look\nforthe sacred object, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:39.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So all this happened\nin my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's such a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do something with\nmy spiritual powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll find the Monkey God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, my powers are only\neffective from morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I wanted to have a place\nto stay tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're being tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure about\ntelling such a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something fishy\nabout all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How pitiful, though.\NFalling for such a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:24.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry up and do something,\nor you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:25.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With my hand like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't use the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,remains stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stone-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a good thing, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have anotherweapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you picturing,\nyou two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Inuyasha is stuck like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going back home\nto the present time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey wait, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This may be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you picturing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:32.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall I suck up the rock\nwith my Wind Tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you just suck up\nthe rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I stop in the nick\nof time, it may work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll open my Wind Tunnel\nlike this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,suck up the rock and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just as you get near it,\NI'll close my...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:45.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this "huh"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... if you're half\nsucked in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you imagining?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:00.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I WILL NOT\nsuck you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to stay\nwith me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, isn't it lonely all\nby yourself out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I'm not, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go if I'm a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what a problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there anotherway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:44.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is about all we\ncan offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And... what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:02.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Weren't these vegetables\ngrown in the fields here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is unmistakably the glow\nfrom ourMonkey God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as he said in my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dark and dank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Small and suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With a smell of vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The field is the only place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He must be buried deep\nunderground!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright! We'll turn the village\nupside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd like to see something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:40.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The pickling stone has a glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the sacred object!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monkey God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Glow?\N- We don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a terrible thing\nto do to the sacred object!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:53.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You DID steal it, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I found it on the\noutskirts of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be a perfect\nweight for pickling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you found it right\noutside the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:02.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:06.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sacred object was kept in\nthe shrine deep in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We sprites guarded it dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! Even that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:15.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We desperately took the sacred object\nout of the burning shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've brought it farenough.\NIt should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... acorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lots and lots of'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look... overhere, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:45.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In otherwords,\nyou forgot all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:48.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, the purification water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monkey God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've longed to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It reeked of vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:07.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monkey God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has anything strange happened\nin my absence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:14.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Not a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yep, they forgot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you build a new shrine\nand make offerings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:30.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Monkey God will\nprotect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:37.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Inuyasha,\nthat the weight is off yourhand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! What a waste of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:45.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shrewd young girl!\NYou did well to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no... your dream messages\nwere so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You three were\njust too stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:58.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You thought it was\nunderground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:02.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to get out\nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was concerned about\nthe strange occurrence outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Strange occurrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shortly after I was placed\nin the pickling tub,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:15.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I felt an awful evil aura,\nthe likes of which I had neverfelt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:19.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,pass over the skies above\nthe village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monkey God, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I felt its presence while\NI was in the pickling tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did itgo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It didn't just pass over completely.\NIt suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.\NIt's Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:48.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma headed in the direction\nof the ox and tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ox and tiger?\NThat's northeast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't pinpointexactly\nwhere it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We know which way to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:21.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Acorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:25.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Scared ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moon ya, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moon ya, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were some adversaries, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just pesky monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:06.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We head northeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.37,0:23:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She must've been exhausted with\nall this searching for Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:55.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her cold got worse\nand she's running a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:57.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had her return home to her time.\NWas that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've got medicine and doctors\nthere... I hope she recovers quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:04.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha went back to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To wish herwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like he's the kind of guy\nto do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.28,0:24:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Nursing Battle of the Rival Lovers"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.72,0:24:14.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rivals? Whose?
